{
  "stem": "3631.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because they-- they had to negotiate with Germans, sometimes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans came very often and they came to the Jews when they needed something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed coffee, so you had to get them some coffee and the-- the people in Krakow in the Judenrat, they still had the connections in town to be able to get these things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it's like-- it's like a city administration in an occupied country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's say you take Paris, when-- when-- when France was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sure the administration was not-- not very well-liked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother worked in a-- that factory-- one of the factories that I think Josef [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Modridge ?] had.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a German-- I think a Viennese German-- who was friendly to us and who-- who supplied us with more food than we could get, and they had hundreds of women working there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had factories for-- and I don't remember whether it was in ghetto in Plaszow-- made brushes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] It was-- you needed-- they made handmade brushes, scrubbing brushes and so on, and the children worked there, you know, the grown up children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and that was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we had other workshops, plumbing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Jews were very good shoemakers in the ghetto, especially in Krak-- in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had workshops where-- the Germans liked high boots.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Jews are excellent makers of these high-- the upper-- upper parts of boots.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all the SS men, the SS officers all came into Plaszow and got these boots, which the Germans had made for them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a crazy world, I'm telling you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's hard to-- hard to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father, I don't really remember it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
